== Usage ==
{{markup
|<nowiki>{{Update inline|date</nowiki>{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}<nowiki>}}</nowiki>|{{Update inline|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|<nowiki>{{Update inline|?=yes|date=</nowiki>{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}<nowiki>}}</nowiki>|{{Update inline|?=yes|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|<nowiki>{{Update inline|reason=But they never mentioned it again...|date=</nowiki>{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}<nowiki>}}</nowiki>|{{Update inline|reason=But they never mentioned it again...|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
|<nowiki>{{Update inline|reason=Does this still hold after so many years?|?=yes|date=</nowiki>{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}<nowiki>}}</nowiki>|{{Update inline|reason=Does this still hold after so many years?|?=yes|date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}
}}

This template will add [[WP:mainspace|mainspace]] articles to [[:Category:Wikipedia articles in need of updating]] (this category is not populated by pages in other [[WP:namespace|namespace]]s).

